# 1.6 Types of SEO

## 1. On-Page SEO

Website ke andar hone wali optimization.

Examples:

* Title Tag
* Meta Description
* Headings
* Images
* Keywords
* Internal Links

---

## 2. Off-Page SEO

Website ke bahar hone wali optimization.

Examples:

* Backlinks
* Social Sharing
* Business Listings
* Brand Mentions

---

## 3. Technical SEO

Website ki technical performance improve karna.

Examples:

* Sitemap
* robots.txt
* HTTPS
* Website Speed
* Mobile Friendly Design
* Structured Data

---

## 4. Local SEO

Local businesses ke liye SEO.

Examples:

* Fire Extinguisher Mumbai
* Fire Extinguisher Virar
* Fire Safety Vasai

---

## 5. E-commerce SEO

Online shopping websites ke liye SEO.

Examples:

* Product Pages
* Category Pages
* Product Reviews
* Product Filters

---

# 1.7 Google Ranking Factors

Google website ko rank karne ke liye 200+ ranking signals use karta hai.

Important factors:

* High Quality Content
* Relevant Keywords
* Website Speed
* Mobile Friendly Design
* User Experience (UX)
* Quality Backlinks
* HTTPS Security
* Fresh Content
* Local Signals
* Customer Reviews

---

# 1.8 Common SEO Myths

❌ SEO ek baar kar diya to lifetime ranking mil jayegi.

✔ SEO ek continuous process hai.

---

❌ Zyada Keywords = Better Ranking

✔ Keyword Stuffing Google ko pasand nahi hai.

---

❌ Sirf Backlinks hi Ranking karte hain.

✔ Content + Technical SEO + Backlinks sab equally important hain.

---

❌ SEO se 7 din me result aa jata hai.

✔ SEO generally 3–6 months ya usse bhi zyada time leta hai, competition aur website quality ke hisaab se.

---

