# 1.10 Important SEO Terms

**SEO** – Search Engine Optimization

**SERP** – Search Engine Results Page

**Keyword** – User dwara search kiya gaya word ya phrase.

**Organic Traffic** – Free visitors jo search engines se aate hain.

**Googlebot** – Google ka crawler.

**Crawling** – Website ko discover aur read karna.

**Indexing** – Website ko Google database me save karna.

**Ranking** – Search results me website ki position.

**Backlink** – Kisi dusri website se milne wala link.

**CTR (Click Through Rate)** – Search result dekhne wale users me se kitne log click karte hain.

